reviews.text:
It's Starbucks.   Overpriced coffee.  Good coffee,   but like I said, overpriced.

The fancy whipped cream drinks?   That's not coffee.
Good for a drink, a snack or even a light meal. I grab quick food there often as an alternative to McDonald's.
Nice place to chat with my friends or just hanging around to finish my work

They give only 30' minutes of WiFi. I spent 49 dollars in a tea and a small muffin just to be able to work here and I found I can only use WiFi for half an hour. The more expensive free-wifi in the world!
Good coffee a reasonable price
